{"tid":1892452,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳門：滯留湖北澳門居民正身處祖國土地 國家對他們相當關懷照顧","createTime":"2020-02-22T14:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T05:20:17.000Z","uid":5195,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6743bf603f882d06b7fb5b12a5c66ac3fd29ba","tid":1892452,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"現時仍然有124名澳門居民身處湖北省18個縣市，有在鄂本澳居民反映，糧食開始短缺，冀特區政府協助返澳。旅遊局執照及監察廳廳長陳露在例行記者會上強調，該批在鄂本澳居民正身處在自己的祖國、自己的土地上，國家對澳門居民相當地關懷及照顧。<br />\n<br />\n她亦指，自疫情開始至今，特區政府一直希望將他們帶回本澳，一直未有停止過協調及溝通工作。但指若匆忙地帶他們回澳，如過程中受到任何不安全因素影響「大家都唔想」，必須要以居民安全作首要考量，籲社會放心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e5b409a4021f9759312d96720ca3d3eccc7199","tid":1892452,"uid":275885,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"香港都同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7b26d5f9cee23f7b8fd8c25f45416bd914006a","tid":1892452,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"9a2511572929c21cb5d7a45d0d8d929be46b928b","tid":1892452,"uid":37869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"林鄭可以照抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10b4db2852837974830181da59207eb629c2469","tid":1892452,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"直接聯署白宮要求youtube解釋點解限制言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=342e49c4\" data-auto-li